J.J. Fish & Chicken in the Plaza at 55th & Wentworth is a superb fast food restaurant. They provide quality service and their catering is excellent. When you call in an order they text message you notifying you that it is ready. The atmosphere of the restaurant is peaceful, it is very clean, their cooks are consistent; and I highly recommend their tilapia and whitefish. My overall experiences with J.J. Fish & Chicken have been all good and they are worthy of consideration for fast food dining, take out and catering.
